    public class ExternalTreeItemFieldSelectorPlugin
extends ExternalDocumentFieldSelectorPlugin
    External document(s) selector field plugin for tree item data from external data backend. This class simply exstends ExternalDocumentFieldSelectorPlugin to show a different implementation of the dialog when user clicks on the browse button.
